# LuminariMUD Code Ownership
#
# This file defines code ownership for the LuminariMUD project.
# Each line is a file pattern followed by the owner(s).
# Order matters: later patterns override earlier ones.
#
# For details: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owners (applies to everything unless overridden)
* @LuminariMUD/core-team

